                    "QuestionTag": "ReadinessToEngage-Commitment-Statement",
                    "Label": "Upload your organisation's commitment statement template",
                    "ShortLabel": "",
                    "QuestionBodyText": "<p class='govuk-body' id='rte-commitment-statement'>Your organisation can <a href='https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/792229/ESFA_Commitment_Statement_v1_reissued_.xlsx' target='_blank'>use ESFA's commitment statement</a>, use one from a third party or create its own.</p><p class='govuk-body'>It must include:</p><ul class='govuk-list govuk-list--bullet'><li>the planned content and schedule for training</li><li>what is expected and offered by the employer, the training organisation and the apprentice</li><li>a section for the employer, apprentice and training organisation to sign</li></ul><p class='govuk-body'>Find out more about the commitment statement in <a href='https://www.gov.uk/guidance/apprenticeship-funding-rules-for-training-providers/what-is-an-apprenticeship#rule-p65' target='_blank'>the apprenticeship funding rules (opens in a new window)</a>.</p><p class='govuk-body'>The file must be a PDF and smaller than 5MB.</p>",
